high_descs: Go to the desk in front of you.
Pick up the cell phone on the desk that is closest to the TV.
Step back from the desk.
Place the cell phone in the back, right corner of the top, right dresser.
Move over to the center of the desk, to your left.
Pick up the other cell phone that is to the left of the book on the desk.
Move over to the right side of the desk again.
Place the cell phone in the top, right drawer of the desk, in front of the other cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phone's in the desk drawer.

high_descs: Move a step forward to the desk.
Pick up the cell phone from the back side of the desk.
Hold the cell phone and take a step to the left.
Open the top right drawer and place the cell phone inside. Shut the drawer.
Look up to the desk.
Pick up the cell phone from the center of the desk.
Hold the cell phone and take a step back.
Open the top right drawer and place the cell phone inside. Shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones in the drawer.

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the desk in front of you.
Pick up the cell phone that is to the right of the book on the desk.
With the cell phone in hand move so you can open the top right desk drawer.
Open the drawer.  Put the cell phone in the drawer on the right side towards the back and close it.
Move over so you are in front of the cell phone on the desk that is to the left of the book.
Pick up the cell phone that is to the left of the book on the desk.
Move so you are on the right side of the desk and can open the top right drawer with the cell phone in hand.
Open the drawer and place the cell phone on the right side in front of the cell phone that is in there.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones in the drawer.
